<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Ssl on 大大的小蜗牛</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/tags/ssl/</link><description>Recent content in Ssl on 大大的小蜗牛</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>© 2006 - 2024 &lt;span class='inline-block'>&lt;a href='https://www.eallion.com/copyright/' target='_blank'>eallion.com&lt;/a> All Rights Reserved&lt;/span>. &lt;span class='inline-block'>&lt;a href='https://beian.miit.gov.cn/' target='_blank'>浙ICP备16031768号-2&lt;/a>&lt;/span></copyright><lastBuildDate>Sun, 25 Sep 2016 00:19:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.eallion.com/tags/ssl/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Destination Host Prohibited</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/destination-host-prohibited/</link><pubDate>Sun, 25 Sep 2016 00:19:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/destination-host-prohibited/</guid><description>这篇文章介绍了如何解决“Destination Host Prohibited”的问题。问题出现的原因是由于服务器上的iptables配置导致的。文章给出的解决方法是检查filter表中的FORWARD链，查看是否包含有相关的行，如果有则删除该行。作者提供了删除该行的命令示例。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/destination-host-prohibited/featured.png"/></item><item><title>正在更换 SSL 证书</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/ssl-change/</link><pubDate>Sat, 19 Dec 2015 17:29:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/ssl-change/</guid><description>这篇文章介绍了一个网站正在更换SSL证书，可能会在浏览时出现风险提示。作者强调该网站只是个人博客，不会给读者带来任何损失，但也提醒读者平时注意上网安全。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/ssl-change/featured.png"/></item></channel></rss>